{"tid":1045611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想買水晶戴改善下溝女運程 水晶師介紹左隻水晶畀我","createTime":"2019-03-03T16:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T17:30:54.000Z","uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c118fb34b6fb8a95e02e7eeb8bca888b259b7020","tid":1045611,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"一行入去 我都未出聲 佢就即刻企起身啦話有隻水晶襯我襯到絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超級七 Super Seven (硬度7）<br />\n<br />\n超級七 Super Seven，因它全面性的功效和見效速度，是本公司最熱賣的水晶之一。它又稱神聖七，產量極少，是高頻率水晶能量石，因內含紫水晶、茶水晶、鈦晶、黃磷鐵礦、針鐵礦、纖維礦、金紅石，七種礦物的共生礦，因此它被稱為 超級七Super Seven。超級七有不同質素，尤以裡面的髮針和礦片較多及閃的能量為最強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3172a86ef955bccedf50e7573c33812097495e50","tid":1045611,"uid":228296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"006f7d5f323babeb919f78e017d1ffcba9ec9473","tid":1045611,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj